divs: Sighting DetailsI saw two of them with binoculars the first one was like a stretch diamond color like a black and shinny too turning slowly thee second one was a cyclinder with a square on the bottom but nut a true square had like a tail on it color was like a black crome the square on the bottom was gray with black lines in it runnimg thur it , also it was just drifting in the sky when the sun hit it was really shiny i could see this with my binoculars i watch it for thirty minute It was like i was in the movies,i never seen anything like this also i was with two other poeple and we shared the binoculars i felt like i was seeing something out of this world then ill call my brother ans he tracked it coming over the resevior for about thirty mintues then he saw a jet fighter flying real low to the ground , the jet was going in the direction of the object then he lost it from his site. there were all kinds of people pulled over on highway 152
